This is the required software for compiling the buz_tools:

.) The precompiled binaries are for glibc2.0/libjpeg6/Kernel 2.2.10

.) A 2.2.x kernel (the driver needs it). 

.) libjpeg6
(libjpeg .... is included in RedHat)

.) The GLib library - http://www.gtk.org
(libglib .... is included in RedHat)

And for people who want to use ALSA support (optional):
.) ALSA driver/lib (http://alsa.jcu.cz)

/Gernot (gz@lysator.liu.se)
